<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SafeTracker: Sweepstakes | Safety Rankings & Winner Reports</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Compare sweepstakes, giveaway, and rewards sites by safety signals, transparency, winner proof, entry traps, and marketing pressure.">
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow,max-image-preview:large,max-snippet:-1">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/safetracker-icon.png">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:title" content="SafeTracker: Sweepstakes">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Independent safety rankings, site reviews, winner reports, and unsubscribe help for sweepstakes entrants.">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/">
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph": [
      {"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/#website","name":"SafeTracker: Sweepstakes","alternateName":["SafeTracker Sweepstakes","SafeTracker"],"url":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/"},
      {"@type":"Organization","@id":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/#organization","name":"SafeTracker: Sweepstakes","url":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/assets/safetracker-icon.png","width":512,"height":512}},
      {"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/#page","url":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/","name":"SafeTracker: Sweepstakes Safety Rankings","dateModified":"{{ last_updated_iso }}","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://sweeps.safetrackerhub.com/#website"}}
    ]
  }
  </script>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/site.css">
  <style>
    th { position:sticky; top:0; background:#134e4a; color:white; z-index:10; }
    tr:nth-child(even) { background:#f0fdfa; }

    /* Distressed ScamFactor stamp */
    .scamfactor-badge {
      display: block;
      width: clamp(8rem, 18vw, 11rem);
      height: auto;
      transform: rotate(-3deg);
      transform-origin: center;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 1px rgb(127 29 29 / 0.12));
      cursor: help;
    }
    .scamfactor-column-badge {
      display: block;
      width: 5.5rem;
      height: auto;
      margin-inline: auto;
      transform: rotate(-3deg);
    }

    /* Score pills */
    .score-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 2.4rem;
      height: 2rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      cursor: help;
    }
    .score-low    { background: #e5f4ea; color: #1f6f3d; border-color: #70bf87; }
    .score-midlow { background: #eef4d8; color: #596b13; border-color: #aec657; }
    .score-mid    { background: #fff4cf; color: #785d00; border-color: #d6b62f; }
    .score-high   { background: #ffead8; color: #914910; border-color: #e48a2b; }
    .score-danger { background: #fbe2df; color: #8b2d25; border-color: #d44b3e; }

    /* Simple tooltip enhancement */
    [title] {
      position: relative;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 min-h-screen">

  <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-800 to-teal-600 text-white shadow-lg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> SafeTracker: Sweepstakes
        </h1>
        <p class="text-teal-100 text-sm mt-1">
          Ranked from lowest to highest ScamFactor • Rescored weekly • Updated {{ last_updated }}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">

    <!-- Safety -->
    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6 text-sm">
      <strong class="text-amber-800">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle mr-1"></i> Never pay to claim a prize.
      </strong>
      Real sweepstakes are free. Use a burner email.
    </div>

    <details class="seo-guide seo-guide-disclosure" open>
      <summary aria-labelledby="safe-sweepstakes-guide">
        <span>
          <span class="section-kicker">Use the rankings wisely</span>
          <strong id="safe-sweepstakes-guide">How to find legitimate sweepstakes—and avoid prize scams</strong>
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="seo-guide-body">
        <div class="seo-guide-columns">
          <p>A legitimate sweepstakes clearly identifies its sponsor, provides official rules, explains eligibility and entry limits, and never requires a winner to pay a fee to receive a prize. SafeTracker compares platforms and directories using those signals, along with winner evidence, fulfillment complaints, entry friction, realistic opportunity, and marketing pressure.</p>
          <p>The ScamFactor score runs from 1 to 10, with lower scores indicating fewer concerns. It is a comparison tool, not a promise that every promotion on a platform is safe. Check each promotion’s official rules, use a dedicated email address, and be cautious when a form requests sensitive information before you have been verified as a winner.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seo-guide-links">
          <a href="methodology.html">Read our complete scoring methodology →</a>
          <a href="site-types.html">Understand each type of sweepstakes site →</a>
          <a href="winners.html">Search reported sweepstakes winners →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Top CTAs -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
      <a href="https://www.swagbucks.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored"
         class="bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center font-semibold shadow transition">
        Start with Swagbucks → Reliable Daily Earnings
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.mondosweeps.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center font-semibold shadow transition">
        Try Mondosweeps → Best Daily $25 Chance
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.pch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center font-semibold shadow transition">
        Enter PCH → America’s Most Trusted Big Prizes
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- ScamFactor Header -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border p-4 mb-6">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-teal-800 mb-2 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <img src="assets/scamfactor-stamp.png"
             alt="ScamFactor"
             class="scamfactor-badge"
             width="1774"
             height="887"
             title="ScamFactor is our proprietary score (1-10). Lower is better."
             loading="eager">
        <span class="text-xs bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-normal">
          Higher = more red flags, hidden fees, aggressive spam
        </span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-2 text-xs">
        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-2 rounded" title="Do they clearly show winners and official rules?">30% Transparency & Winner Proof</div>
        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-2 rounded" title="How often do people report receiving prizes vs complaints?">25% Fulfillment & Complaints</div>
        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-2 rounded" title="Are there hidden requirements, paid entries, or hard-to-find free methods?">20% Entry Model & Gotchas</div>
        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-2 rounded" title="How realistic is it to actually win something meaningful?">15% Win Opportunity Realism</div>
        <div class="bg-teal-50 p-2 rounded" title="How aggressive is the email/SMS marketing after signing up?">10% Marketing Aggressiveness</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Table -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow border overflow-x-auto mb-10">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left" title="Overall ranking based on ScamFactor">#</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Site</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Type</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-center" title="Lower score = more legitimate and better chance of a real win">
              <img src="assets/scamfactor-stamp.png"
                   alt="ScamFactor"
                   class="scamfactor-column-badge"
                   width="1774"
                   height="887">
            </th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Prizes (examples)</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Draw Frequency</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Unsubscribe</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Major Red Flags</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-3 text-center">Link</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for s in sites %}
          <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 hover:bg-teal-50/50"
              data-category="{{ s.theme|default('other') }}"
              data-verified="{{ last_updated }}"
              data-review-url="reviews/{{ s.slug }}.html">
            <td class="px-3 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-500">{{ s.rank }}</td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 font-medium">{{ s.name }}</td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-xs"><a class="category-badge" href="site-types.html#{{ s.theme|default('other') }}">{{ s.theme|default('other')|replace('-', ' ')|title }}</a></td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-center">
              {% set score = s.score|float %}
              {% if score <= 2 %}
                <span class="score-pill score-low" title="Excellent – Low risk, transparent, realistic chances">{{ s.score }}</span>
              {% elif score <= 4 %}
                <span class="score-pill score-midlow" title="Good – Generally legitimate with minor issues">{{ s.score }}</span>
              {% elif score <= 6 %}
                <span class="score-pill score-mid" title="Average – Some red flags or aggressive marketing">{{ s.score }}</span>
              {% elif score <= 8 %}
                <span class="score-pill score-high" title="Caution – Higher risk of spam or poor fulfillment">{{ s.score }}</span>
              {% else %}
                <span class="score-pill score-danger" title="High Risk – Significant red flags or deceptive practices">{{ s.score }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-xs max-w-xs">{{ s.prizes }}</td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-xs">{{ s.draw }}</td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-xs text-teal-700">
              <a class="unsubscribe-detail-link" href="reviews/{{ s.slug }}.html#unsubscribe">Unsubscribe info →</a>
            </td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-xs text-red-700">{{ s.redFlags }}</td>
            <td class="px-3 py-3 text-center">
              {% if s.link and s.link != "#" %}
                <a href="{{ s.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline font-medium">Visit</a>
              {% else %}
                <span class="text-slate-400">—</span>
              {% endif %}
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center text-xs text-slate-500 py-6 border-t">
      Data last refreshed {{ last_updated }}. Always verify official rules on each site.<br>
      Some links may be affiliate links. Rankings are never paid. · SafeTracker: Sweepstakes v1.2
    </footer>
  </main>
  <script src="assets/tracker.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
